    <name>AndroMDA: The Open Source MDA Tool</name>
    <description>
         AndroMDA (pronounced: andromeda) is an open source code generation framework that follows the Model Driven Architecture  
        (MDA) paradigm. It takes model(s) from CASE-tool(s) and generates fully deployable applications and other components.
    </description>
